name: Social Network InsuranceToBe
short_description:
Online insurance is a program aimed at easy search of insurance info in real time. I2Be is always available online!

What is Online Insurance and how can it make your life easier? Our project is a social network, focused on the various needs of assurance service consumers.

Since 2006 we help thousands of people find the best solutions for risk management, as well as the most qualified agents and coverage brokers. We work to maintain a favorable direction of professional relationships on both sides. A satisfied client, broker and insurance agent is our ultimate goal, as we act according to the formula WIN-WIN!
summary: nsurance To Be Online - Resource for Online Insurance Needs!
